{"tid":471391,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[又中伏] 巴絲小心, 去深水埗大鋪買Game照樣比人呃","createTime":"2017-11-17T08:08:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T12:23:36.000Z","uid":21267,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6927bf5a16642df4917fea8907ecb3a9de1e567e","tid":471391,"uid":21267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T08:08:40.000Z","msg":"巴打絲打們，小弟今日去在深水埗一間 老任authorities dealer 度買隻Mario Odyssey, 去得佢個度就梗係想買中文版, 好啦買完比錢走。當我行到落去地鐵站先見到係日文版封面。咁我就梗係返返去同佢換啦(個一下我真係真心覺得佢拎錯)。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去到個位啊姐話： 係丫，個個係日本封面，可上上網update.  <br />\n我: 我要返中文版封面。 <br />\n姐: 你幾時買? (質疑加西語氣) <br />\n我: 啱啱買囉.即時show 埋張單. <br />\n姐: 乜我地重有日版封面咩( 死死地氣換比我) <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我個一下就知佢特登比呢隻日版我。DLLM 去得你度買唔通啱你嗰度買得貴啲咩⋯⋯ 我係識update中文，但係我比得錢就梗係買我想要既嘢，呢間野我之前都聽過其他巴打/絲打話過，打開門做生意貪個小便宜， 做衰自己個名，重要係authorised dealer。各位巴打/絲打自己衡量下仲喺唔喺佢哋度買嘢啦。"},{"pid":"507722f5693a3781b3e69cd70785a2ec58660f96","tid":471391,"uid":21267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T09:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a507625fdbb0c11e46682a5430d525765a07f5","tid":471391,"uid":38191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T09:25:39.000Z","msg":"唔開名？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21fb4163b4663da873f883e7f01f41860e6815b","tid":471391,"uid":21267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T10:19:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1ad7166a46484bd8c51fbce61a6f0c0ba2d349","tid":471391,"uid":21267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T11:24:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7296beb388ca942a39185cc58253b5d159ab1bf","tid":471391,"uid":21267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T11:58:29.000Z","ms